fields.name: Brown Clay Wall Art
fields.description: An bespoke sculpted wall art piece with artistic engravings, made from rough brown clay, ideal for the family home.

fields.name: Set of 3 Dip Pots
fields.description: A set of 3 uniquely made small pots, ideal for dips or spices. Comes in a range of different colours.

fields.name: Oval Vase
fields.description: A uniquely hand built oval shaped vase, ideal for storing flowers and plants. Made with "Raku" pottery technique in fired kiln.

fields.name: Keepsake Box
fields.description: A handmade ceramic keepsake box for your personal possessions or keepsakes. Constructed using slab building techniques using white clay.

fields.name: 3 Color Coil Pot
fields.description: A handmade 3 coloured vase using the coil pot technique, garaunteed to brighten up any shelf!

fields.name: October Throwing Class
fields.description: Book a place in our October Throwing Class where you can try out making some pottery on our throwing wheels. Places limited to 10 students!

fields.name: Holy Water Font
fields.description: A small custom made holy water font for the home, made from porcelain-type white clay. Hole included for fixing the wall, screw and fixings not included with this item.

fields.name: 3 Panelled Art Piece
fields.description: An artistic wall art piece in 3 related sections depicting a nautical theme. Custom made from custom designs, a beautiful addition to any wall! Pieces not sold individually, must be sold as set of 3.

fields.name: Business Card Holder
fields.description: A custom made business card holder, ideal for storing all your various collected business cards. Looks good at the front of anyones desk! Available in blue presently, but more colours available in near future.

fields.name: Butter Dish
fields.description: A custom made butter dish, made from brown clay and decorated with different slip colours, ideal for any dinner table!

fields.name: Button Tea Coasters
fields.description: A set of 4 differently coloured tea coasters, ideal for brightening up any kitchen table! Not sold individually, sold only as set of 4.

fields.name: The Dark Gnome
fields.description: A custom made garden gnome using dark colours and Raku firing technique, interesting piece to place in your garden!

fields.name: House Name Wall Plaque
fields.description: A custom made wall plaque for any wall area at front of your property. Fittings and fixings not included.

fields.name: Whale Candle Holder
fields.description: A custom made candle holder, made in the shape of a whales body. Ideal piece for windowsills of coastal properties!

fields.name: Bird House
fields.description: A custom made bird house, ideal for any garden!

fields.name: November Raku Class
fields.description: Book a place in our November Raku Class where you can try out making some pottery using our Raku kilns. Places limited to 10 students!

fields.review_text: Really nice piece of work, well designed and executed!
Great item, will buy more again soon!
